title.narrative: Strengthening the Government of Afghanistan's Statistical Capacity

description.narrative: This activity (Strengthening the Government of Afghanistan's Statistical Capacity) is a component of Statistical Adviser Support to Central Statistics Office reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £1,206,478. This component benefits Afghanistan, and works in the following sector(s): Statistical capacity building. The start date is 04-10-2009 and the end date is 30-03-2017.
